Package: enigma2-plugin-extensions-fritz-mon
Version: 1.0.0
Section: base
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: madoe21 <https://github.com/madoe21>
Description: FritzMon – Fritz!Box Network Monitor for Enigma2
 Shows all devices on the Fritz!Box network with IP, MAC address,
 connection type and online status. Uses the TR-064 SOAP API.
Depends: enigma2
